 Nominations 2019: The Complete List |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/oscar-nominations-2019-list-1203112405/ |accessdate=January 22, 2019 |work=Variety |date=January 22, 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===[[British Academy Film Award]]s===\n{| class=wikitable width=90%\n! width=3%| Year\n! width=27%| Nominated work\n! width=56%| Category\n! width=9%| Result\n! width=5%|{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n| [[53rd British Academy Film Awards|1999]]\n| ''[[The Truman Show]]''\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Film|Best Film]]\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=BAFTAs 1999: Film|url=http://awards.bafta.org/award/1999/film/film|publisher=British Academy of Film and Television Arts|accessdate=February 1, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[56th British Academy Film Awards|2002]]\n| ''[[Iris (2001 film)|Iris]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[BAFTA Award for Best British Film|Best British Film]]\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=BAFTAs 2002: British Film of the Year|url=http://awards.bafta.org/award/2002/film/alexander-korda-award-for-the-outstanding-british-film-of-the-year|publisher=British Academy of Film and Television Arts|accessdate=February 1, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[57th British Academy Film Awards|2003]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''The Hours''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=BAFTAs 2003: Film|url=http://awards.bafta.org/award/2003/film|publisher=British Academy of Film and Television Arts|accessdate=February 1, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Film\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[61st British Academy Film Awards|2007]]\n| ''[[Notes on a Scandal]]''\n| Best British Film\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=BAFTAs 2007: British Film of the Year|url=http://awards.bafta.org/award/2007/film/alexander-korda-award-for-the-outstanding-british-film-of-the-year|publisher=British Academy of Film and Television Arts|accessdate=February 1, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[62nd British Academy Film Awards|2008