90076/golden-globes-2014-complete-list-of-nominations|accessdate=October 25, 2017|work=E! News|date=December 12, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Winners & Nominees 2014|url=http://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/2014|publisher=The Golden Globes|accessdate=February 1, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Inside Llewyn Davis]]''\n| rowspan=\"3\"|Best Motion Picture \u2013 Musical or Comedy\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[72nd Golden Globe Awards|2015]]\n| ''The Grand Budapest Hotel''\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|title=Golden Globe Winners 2015: Complete List|url=https://variety.com/2015/film/news/golden-globe-winners-2015-updated-list-1201400369/|accessdate=October 25, 2017|work=Variety|date=January 11, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Best Motion Picture \u2013 Musical or Comedy: 2015|url=http://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/best-motion-picture-musical-or-comedy/all-years#year-2015|publisher=The Golden Globes|accessdate=February 1, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[75th Golden Globe Awards|2018]]\n| ''[[Lady Bird (film)|Lady Bird]]''\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lopez|first1=Ricardo|title='Lady Bird' Wins Best Picture Comedy, Giving Greta Gerwig Her Moment in the Spotlight|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/lady-bird-wins-golden-globe-best-motion-picture-comedy-1202655168/|accessdate=January 8, 2018|work=Variety|date=January 7, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[76th Golden Globe Awards|2019]]\n| ''[[Isle of Dogs (film)|Isle of Dogs]]''\n| [[Golden Globe Award for Best Animated Feature Film|Best Motion Picture \u2013 Animated]]\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news |title=Golden Globe Nominations: Complete List |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/golden-globe-nominations-2019-1203082075/ |accessdate=December 9, 2018 |work=Variety |date=December 6, 2018}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===[[Gotham Award]]s===\n{| class=wikitable width=90%\n! width=3%| Year\n! width=27%| Nominated work\n! width=56%| Category\n! width=9%| R