ses.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.levante-emv.com/comunitat-valenciana/2020/03/03/coronavirus-valencia-infectados/1984792.html|title=Sanidad confirma en Val\u00e8ncia el primer fallecido con coronavirus en Espa\u00f1a |date=3 March 2020 |access-date=3 March 2020 |newspaper=Levante |publisher=Grupo Prensa Ib\u00e9rica Media |language=es}}</ref> After a forensic investigation, a man who had been infected with coronavirus in the Hospital Arnau de Vilanova died on 13 February in Valencia.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.abc.es/espana/comunidad-valenciana/abci-hombre-habia-contagiado-coronavirus-murio-13-febrero-valencia-202003032010_noticia.html|title=Un hombre que se hab\u00eda contagiado de coronavirus muri\u00f3 el 13 de febrero en Valencia |newspaper=[[ABC (newspaper)|ABC]]|publisher=Diario ABC, S.L.|date=3 March 2020|access-date=3 March 2020|language=es}}</ref>\n* The first death in Madrid took place this day; it was reported on 5 March after a forensic analysis.<ref name=autogenerated2>{{cite news |url=https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20200305/coronavirus-ultimas-noticias-directo-7817968|title=Coronavirus: Tercer muerto en Espa\u00f1a. \u00daltimas noticias en DIRECTO|date=5 March 2020 |access-date=5 March 2020 |newspaper=[[elperiodic.com]] |publisher=Editorial Digital 2014 S.L. |language=es}}</ref><ref name=autogenerated4>{{cite news |url=https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/4176043/0/mujer-99-anos-primera-victima-coronavirus-madrid/ |title=Muere una mujer de 99 a\u00f1os en Madrid con coronavirus: primera v\u00edctima en la capital y tercera en Espa\u00f1a |date=5 March 2020 |access-date=5 March 2020 |newspaper=[[20 Minutos]] |publisher=20 Minutos Editora S.L. |language=es}}</ref>\n\n;4 March\n* In Asturias a new positive case was reported, amounting 4 cases.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.europapress.es/asturias/noticia-asturias-confirma-cuarto-positivo-coronavirus-20200304132401.html |title=Asturias confirma su cuarto positivo en Coronavirus, un hombre de 48 a\u00f1os |date=4 March 2020 |access-date=4 March 2020 |newspaper=[[Europa Press]] |publisher=Europa Press Noticias S.A. |language=es}}</ref>\n* In [[Aragon]] the first case of coronavirus was confirmed, a 79-year-old man.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.aragondigital.es/2020/03/04/aragon-registra-su-primer-caso-de-coronavirus-en-un-hombre-de-79-anos/ |title=Arag\u00f3n registra su primer caso de coronavirus en un hombre de 79 a\u00f1os a expensas del segundo an\u00e1lisis |date=4 March 2020 |access-date=4 March 2020 |newspaper=[[Arag\u00f3ndigital.es]] |publisher= |language=es}}</ref>\n* In the Balearic Islands, two more confirmed cases, two young men from [[Sa Pobla]] who travelled to Bergamo, making a total of 4 active cases and one recovered.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.cronicabalear.es/2020/03/se-elevan-a-cinco-los-casos-de-coronavirus-en-mallorca/ |title=Se elevan a cinco los casos de coronavirus en Mallorca |date=4 March 2020 |access-date=4 March 2020 |newspaper=[[Cr\u00f3nica Balear]] |publisher= |language=es}}</ref>\n* In the Basque Country 8 another positives bring the total positives to 21, 16 active cases in \u00c1lava, two in Gipuzkoa and three more infected and one death in Vizcaya. 250 people remain in isolation, more than of them a hundred are health professionals.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.deia.eus/actualidad/sociedad/2020/03/04/ascienden-17-casos-coronavirus-euskadi/1022315.html |title=Cuatro nuevos positivos elevan a diecisiete los casos de coronavirus en Euskadi |date=4 March 2020 |access-date=4 March 2020 |newspaper=[[Deia (newspaper)|Deia]] |publisher=Editorial Iparraguirre, S.A. |language=es}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/4175566/0/segundo-muerto-coronavirus-pais-vasco/ |title=Segundo muerto en Espa\u00f1a infectado con coronavirus: un hombre de Bilbao de 82 a\u00f1os que padec\u00eda neumon\u00eda |date=4 March 2020 |access-date=4 March 2020 |newspaper=[[20 Minutos]] |publisher=20 Minutos Edi