iedad/2020/03/05/sanidad-confirma-primer-caso-coronavirus/1261829.html |title=Sanidad confirma el primer caso de coronavirus en Gran Canaria |date=5 March 2020 |access-date=5 March 2020 |newspaper=[[La Provincia-Diario de Las Palmas]] |publisher=Grupo Prensa Ib\u00e9rica Media |language=es}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.europapress.es/islas-canarias/noticia-nuevo-caso-huespedes-hotel-tenerife-eleva-ocho-positivos-canarias-20200305203656.html |title=Un nuevo caso entre los hu\u00e9spedes del hotel de Tenerife eleva a ocho los positivos en Canarias |date=5 March 2020 |access-date=5 March 2020 |newspaper=[[Europa Press]] |publisher=Europa Press Noticias S.A. |language=es}}</ref>\n* In Castile and Le\u00f3n two new cases in [[Tamames]], [[province of Salamanca]], and [[Valladolid]], raise the total positives to 13.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.elnortedecastilla.es/salamanca/sanidad-detecta-positivo-20200305162228-nt.html |title=Sanidad confirma un caso positivo de coronavirus en la localidad salmantina de Tamames |date=5 March 2020 |access-date=5 March 2020 |newspaper=[[El Norte de Castilla]] |publisher= |language=es}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.elnortedecastilla.es/castillayleon/tres-nuevos-afectados-20200304105159-nt.html |title=Dos nuevos casos en Valladolid y Salamanca elevan a trece los afectados por coronavirus en la comunidad |date=5 March 2020 |access-date=5 March 2020 |newspaper=[[El Norte de Castilla]] |publisher= |language=es}}</ref>\n* In Castilla\u2013La Mancha 1 new case in Guadalajara was reported, raising the total to 13.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.encastillalamancha.es/sanidad/un-nuevo-caso-de-coronavirus-y-ya-van-13-en-castilla-la-mancha/ |title=Un nuevo caso de coronavirus, y ya van 13, en Castilla-La Mancha |date=5 March 2020 |access-date=5 March 2020 |newspaper=[[El Caso]] |publisher=ECOS C-LM, S.L. |language=es}}</ref>\n* In Catalonia, 4 new positive cases of coronavirus increase to 32 in total.<ref>{{cite news |url=