ier Ortega Smith da positivo por coronavirus y Vox pide perd\u00f3n por celebrar Vistalegre|publisher=El Mundo|date=10 March 2020|last=Carvajal|first=\u00c1lvaro|language=es|access-date=10 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* After Ortega Smith tested positive for COVID-19, the [[Congress of Deputies]] and the [[Senate of Spain|Senate]] suspended its parliamentary activity for a period of a week and 52 Vox's lawmakers are asked to stay at home.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.elmundo.es/espana/2020/03/10/5e677680fdddff77138b45be.html|title=El Congreso suspende su actividad una semana tras el positivo del diputado Ortega Smith|publisher=El Mundo|date=10 March 2020|last=Cruz|first=Marisa|language=es|access-date=10 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* All direct flights between Spanish and Italian airports suspended until 25 March.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.boe.es/boe/dias/2020/03/10/|title=Bolet\u00edn Oficial del Estado: martes 10 de marzo de 2020|website=boe.es|language=es|date=10 March 2020|access-date=10 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* The first cases in [[province of Tarragona]] are confirmed; two in [[Cambrils]] and two others in [[Salou]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.diaridetarragona.com/tarragona/Cuatro-casos-de-coronavirus-confirmados-en-Tarragona-20200310-0049.html|title=Cuatro casos de coronavirus confirmados en Tarragona|website=Diari de Tarragona|language=es|date=10 March 2020|access-date=10 March 2020}}</ref>\n* An elderly woman from [[Castellser\u00e0]] becomes the first case in [[Province of Lleida]], making all Catalan provinces with cases.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.elpuntavui.cat/societat/article/14-salut/1754984-una-dona-de-castellsera-primer-positiu-en-coronavirus-a-lleida.html|title=Una dona de Castellser\u00e0, primer positiu en coronavirus a Lleida|website=El Punt Avui|language=ca|date=10 March 2020|access-date=10 March 2020}}</ref>\n* The [[Constitutional Court of Spain|Constitutional Court]] suspended its activity for the f