ana-has-coronavirus-source-idUSL8N2B67VA|title=Former NATO chief Javier Solana has coronavirus - source|date=13 March 2020|website=[[Reuters]]}}</ref>\n* In Extremadura, [[Arroyo de la Luz]] was put on lockdown.<ref>{{cite news |title=Vara pide a los vecinos de Arroyo de la Luz \"confianza\" en la decisi\u00f3n de decretar su aislamiento social|trans-title=Vara asks the residents of Arroyo de la Luz to \"trust\" in the decision to decree their social isolation |url=https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/4187495/0/vara-pide-a-los-vecinos-de-arroyo-de-la-luz-confianza-en-la-decision-de-decretar-su-aislamiento-social/ |access-date=14 March 2020 |work=20 minutos |date=13 March 2020 |language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\n;14 March\n[[File:Mesures contra el coronavirus.jpg|thumb|[[Vilafranca del Pened\u00e8s]] bar closed due to the coronavirus]]\n* Vox Deputy [[Antonio Salv\u00e1]] tested positive for COVID-19.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/voxbaleares/status/1238759132347486209|title=.@asalvav Ayer noche he dado positivo en la prueba del COVID-19. Me encuentro bien, cumplo las indicaciones de las autoridades sanitarias y nuestros profesionales sanitarios. Sigo en mi casa de Madrid, no volv\u00ed a Mallorca por precauci\u00f3n. Gracias a todos #quedateencasapic.twitter.com/RBNA88t8iA|last=Baleares|first=V. O. X.|date=14 March 2020|website=@voxbaleares|language=es|access-date=14 March 2020}}</ref>\n* Seville, Granada and Cordoba City Councils, as well as the Region of Murcia, officially cancelled the [[Holy Week in Spain|Holy Week]] festivities.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sevilla.org/actualidad/noticias/comunicado-oficial-sobre-la-semana-santa-de-sevilla-2020|title=Comunicado oficial sobre la Semana Santa de Sevilla 2020|website=Ayuntamiento de Sevilla|language=es|access-date=14 March 2020}}</ref>\n* First death reported in Galicia.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.consalud.es/pacientes/especial-coronavirus/galicia-registra-muerte-coronavirus_75834_102.html|title=Galicia regist